---

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
    display: block;
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -10%;
    right: -5%;
    width: 480px;
    height: 480px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .name-accent {
    color: #38bdf8;
  }
</style>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-tag">Junior-Full-Stack-Developer</div>
      <h1>
        Hi I'm
        <br />
        <span class="name-accent">Charlie Enright</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        I build <strong>data-driven web applications</strong> that help people explore
        landscapes, heritage, and place — combining a background in <strong
          >archaeology and GIS</strong
        > with full-stack development. Based in Wales, UK.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
